::: aim

Provide an example of the TriggerImport node that can be used to import dynamically generated flows.

Demonstrate by converting an RSS feed to a Node-RED flow tab.

:::

::: requirements

This requirements the following Node-RED nodes:

- [introspection](https://flows.nodered.org/node/@gregoriusrippenstein/node-red-contrib-introspection)

